# Global Macro Snapshot

## Growth and Inflation

- IMF: global growth around 3.3% in 2026  
- UNCTAD: more conservative at roughly 2.6%  
- Private houses cluster around 2.8–2.9%

## Interpretation

Q1 2026 should be read not as recovery, but as **managed strain**.

